title: Dying 4 Dummies
author: stratmatt57
pages:
#- Oooooh, hello there kiddies!  Gather around, all yee kiddos and kiddettes.  Let us discuss the benefits of dyes.  
a) They're hella rad!
2) They make your builds look really cool.
c) You look gooder at this game when you understand dyes.  Let's begin!
#- ROSE RED; poppy, rose bush, red tulips. 
ORANGE DYE; Orange tulip.
DANDELION YELLOW; dandelion, sun flower.
CACTUS GREEN; Cactus
BLUE: Lapis Lazuli
LIGHT BLUE; Blue Orchird, lapis & bonemeal.
MAGENTA: Lilac; 2 rose red & 1 lapis lazuli & 
#- 1 bone meal.  OR Purple & Pink dye.
PINK; Peony, Pink tulips.  Rose red & Bone meal
WHITE: Bone meal.
LIGHT GRAY: Azure Bluet, Oxeye Daisy, White Tulip.  OR Bone meal & gray dye.  OR 2 bone meal and 1 ink sac.
BLACK: Ink sac.

#- BROWN: Cocoa beans.

----SECONDARY----
CYAN DYE: Cactus Green & Lapis Lazuli
PURPLE DYE: Rose Red & Lapis Lazuli.
GRAY DYE: Ink sac & Bone meal.
LIME: Cactus Green & Bone Meal.
